Package Description
com.nastenkapusechka.validation
This package contains a validator, annotations, annotation parsers and some helper classes.

This package contains analyzers for annotations
com.nastenkapusechka.validation.annotaions
This package contains annotations that can be hung on the fields of the class
com.nastenkapusechka.validation.util
This package contains several helper classes for the library to work properly.

A package with exceptions that will be thrown if the field does not match the annotation
